 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Strong-jaw:

    Strengthens biting moves to 
  1.5× their power.

  Shell-armor:

    Moves cannot score critical 
  hits against this Pokémon.

  This ability functions identically 
  to battle armor.

  Swift-swim:

    This Pokémon's Speed is doubled 
  during rain.

  This bonus does not count as 
  a stat modifier.


